events.name: アイテムゲットイベント

parameters:
It's true... I wonder what it is? Shall we take a
look?

It seems like something is embedded in the stone
slab. Let's pick it up with a little caution.

I can't quite put it into words, but there's a
strong power flowing in.

It seems like there's no problem, so I
was about to tell you...
Suddenly, a black haze envelops Light.

Doesn't seem like there's anything in particular,
huh?

Really!? Is it really true!? ...Phew, thank
goodness.

However, I can feel some kind of power from that
bracelet.

Should we bring it back just in case it might be a
clue to lift the curse?

Also, if possible, could \n[1] hold onto it? I'm a
little uneasy about it being with me...

I agreed with that opinion and decided to take
care of the black bracelet.

Anyway, I guess this means we've made a little
progress, right?

The sun is starting to set soon, so should we head
back around here for today?

It's true... I wonder what it is? Shall we take a
look?

It seems like something is embedded in the stone
tablet. Let's take it with caution and see what it
is.

I can't quite put it into words, but there's a
strong power flowing in.
As if there's no problem, I tried to convey...
Suddenly, a black haze envelops Light.
It seems like there's no problem, huh?

Is that so? It didn't look like everything was
okay though...

It's true... It doesn't seem like an ordinary
bracelet. I can feel some sort of power.

Should we bring it back just in case it might be a
clue to lift the curse?

Also, if possible, could \n[1] hold onto it? I'm a
little uneasy about having it myself...

I agreed with that opinion and decided to take
care of the black bracelet.
It's better to stop pushing yourself any further.
The sun is starting to set, so let's head back.
Hey hey! \n[1]! There's something over there!

It's true.. I wonder what it is? Shall we take a
look?

It seems like something is embedded in the stone
slab. Let's pick it up with a little caution.

I can't quite put it into words, but there's a
strong power flowing in.

As if to convey that there seems to be no
problem...
Suddenly, a black haze envelops Light.
It seems like there's no particular problem, huh?
Really? Well, if Light says so, then it's fine.

However, I can feel some kind of power from that
bracelet.

Maybe it could be a clue to lift the curse. Should
we bring it back just in case?

Also, if possible, could \n[1] hold onto it? I'm a
little uneasy about having it myself...

I agreed with that opinion and decided to take
care of the black bracelet.

We can handle something like this! Let's keep
going like this!

Well, we did have some gains today, so let's head
back to the village for now!
...\n[1], can you see anything over there?

When I looked in the direction Light indicated, I
could see something shining.

It seems like something is embedded in the stone
slab. I cautiously pick it up, while being a
little wary.

I can't quite put it into words, but there's a
strong power flowing into me.

I was about to say that it seems like there's no
problem...
Suddenly, a black haze envelops Light.

Doesn't seem like there's anything in particular,
huh?

I'll triple check to make sure everything is
really okay.

Yeah, I was a little surprised... but I feel some
kind of power coming from that bracelet.

Should we bring it back just in case it might be a
clue to lift the curse?

Also, if possible, could \n[1] hold onto it? I'm a
little uneasy about having it myself...

I agreed with that opinion and decided to take
care of the black bracelet.

Considering the black haze from earlier, I suggest
we play it safe and return to the village today.

Yeah, it's getting dark, so let's call it a day
around here.
